{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Journey into the Corridor </h2>Step into your reflection as you master the ability switch between your side and the reflected side of the mirror. In this strange set of corridors, the reflected world varies slightly from the normal world. Thankfully in <strong>Corridor VR</strong> you can possess your mirror self to navigate your way through the seemingly endless corridors and find your escape.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722440/extras/FirstGif_Attempt2_.gif?t=1732131930\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Platforming </h2>Because the two worlds are not entirely the same, you'll find plenty of opportunities use this possess ability to quickly swap sides and make it to areas that were once unreachable.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722440/extras/SecondGif_Attempt1_.gif?t=1732131930\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Branching Paths </h2><strong>Corridor VR</strong> offers branching paths through either dungeon themed levels which feature more platforming and deadly traps on top of the normal puzzles, and a Victorian era themed path with less of an emphasis on deadly traps and more on your ability to solve complex puzzles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722440/extras/ThirdGif_Attempt1_.gif?t=1732131930\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Master of the Corridors","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2722440/d79a9d14f0f8a5aa7602c0a7bdef64e2f0db3950.jpg"},{"name":"Into the Corridors","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2722440/f6f6b44542c46ad51f27227519cc6113420afff1.jpg"},{"name":"Getting the hang of it","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2722440/0fd31ec853bceb22b306d48bf5e77ff7840cdb28.jpg"},{"name":"